        <para>The ECM records engine events in two ways, hours and odometer readings.</para>
        <randlist type="bullet">
            <title>Examples</title>
            <item>
                <para>Overheat Hour 1</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Overheat Hour 2</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Overheat Odometer 1</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Overheat Odometer 2</para>
            </item>
        </randlist>
        <para>The ECM stores the two most recent events. Two events could happen in the same hour, and two events could
            happen in the same mile.
        </para>
